{"tid":564824,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖】李嘉欣性感粉紅裙拜年 幼腿返嚟","createTime":"2018-02-18T11:34:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T12:09:54.000Z","uid":48905,"like":123,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"663c23e21f5af642e865bfd5640a0ff4767c8ccf","tid":564824,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T11:34:52.000Z","msg":"李嘉欣前晚和日前老公許晉亨、兒子Jayden，去福臨門吃開年飯，80歲媽媽賀壽並為幫兒子慶祝生日，一身Deep V粉紅皮裙，粉嫰性感，可謂一雪前恥。<br />\n<br />\n李嘉欣早前和兒子過生日，黑色貼身褲，被網友批評「腿好粗」、「胖了」，更指大美人走樣失修云云。她前晚的連身粉紅皮裙，難得露出事業線，A形裙子亦成功修飾大腿，做出腰幼腿長的視效，重現47歲美魔女風情。李嘉欣亦match了粉紅色Valentino 釘珠刺繡手袋，兒子Jayden穿格紋西裝外套、Valentino波鞋搭配墨鏡，傳承媽媽明星作風，架勢十足。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/18/193301_2e21e726e0f5656660bd6ecadfb93a08.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F18%2F193301_2e21e726e0f5656660bd6ecadfb93a08.png&h=22519774&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"> 李嘉欣和老公許晉享、兒子昨晚一齊去福臨門食開年飯。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/18/193338_ff4c1764b5ec874846cda55b89cac0a9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F18%2F193338_ff4c1764b5ec874846cda55b89cac0a9.png&h=ed25faa4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"> 一家三口企定定。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/18/193415_5357cc374f4309d5bd80d9309e085ca9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F18%2F193415_5357cc374f4309d5bd80d9309e085ca9.png&h=d797b64e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"> 就是這一張相, 惹來網民批評李嘉欣腿粗。</span>"},{"pid":"9b4ccb00a0fbf2ab9bbb8811a56f50913d1013e2","tid":564824,"uid":76632,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T11:36:44.000Z","msg":"我"},{"pid":"39d4a07d202ab1103a6ab473a9a8462faf52c3ce","tid":564824,"uid":470,"like":14,"disl